function dStr(x,y,str) cs=string.len(str) for i=0,cs-1 do dChar(x+4*i,y,string.sub(str,i+1,i+1)) end end

end
function rotatePoint(cx, cy, angle, px, py) s = si(angle) c = math.cos(angle) px = px - cx py = py - cy xnew = px * c + py * s ynew = py * c - px * s x = xnew + cx y = ynew + cy return {x=x, y=y} end

function onTick() dx=input.getNumber(1) dy=input.getNumber(2) sx=input.getNumber(3) sy=input.getNumber(4) bearing=input.getNumber(5) rps=input.getNumber(16) temp=input.getNumber(17) compositerange=input.getNumber(18) engineON=input.getBool(2) cam=input.getBool(1) roll=input.getBool(3) alt=input.getBool(4)
range=input.getNumber(6) speed=input.getNumber(7) altgoal=input.getNumber(19)
distance=(math.sqrt((dx-sx)^2+(dy-sy)^2)) --distance in m, using pythagorean theorem output.setNumber(10, distance) output.setNumber(14, bearing)
output.setNumber(15,range) output.setNumber(16,rps) output.setNumber(17,temp) output.setNumber(18,compositerange) output.setNumber(19,altgoal) output.setBool(2,engineON) output.setBool(1,cam) output.setBool(3,roll) output.setBool(4,alt) end

NM=pgB("Night Mode")
Step=pgN("Step size Heading") StepPix=pgN("Pixel step Heading") Hpos=10 RR=200 GG=0 BB=0
function onTick() Deg=igN(1) end
function onDraw() W=screen.getWidth() H=screen.getHeight()
if W>=64 and H>=64 then
NDeg=mc(Deg/Step)*Step NStep=ma(NDeg-Deg)/Step*StepPix sdTB(W/2+NStep-10,H-Hpos-3,20,8,value(NDeg),0,0) screen.drawLine(W/2+NStep,H-Hpos+8,W/2+NStep,H-Hpos+4) if not NM then ssC(RR,GG,BB) else ssC(0,200,0) end screen.drawLine(W/2+NStep-StepPix/2,H-Hpos+8,W/2+NStep-StepPix/2,H-Hpos+6) screen.drawLine(W/2+NStep+StepPix/2,H-Hpos+8,W/2+NStep+StepPix/2,H-Hpos+6) for i=1,mc(W/StepPix) do sdTB(W/2+NStep+i*StepPix-10,H-Hpos-3,20,8,value(NDeg+i*Step),0,0) screen.drawLine(W/2+NStep+i*StepPix,H-Hpos+8,W/2+NStep+i*StepPix,H-Hpos+4) if not NM then ssC(RR,GG,BB) else ssC(200,200,0) end screen.drawLine(W/2+NStep+i*StepPix+StepPix/2,H-Hpos+8,W/2+NStep+i*StepPix+StepPix/2,H-Hpos+6) end
PDeg=mf(Deg/Step)*Step PStep=ma(PDeg-Deg)/Step*StepPix sdTB(W/2-PStep-10,H-Hpos-3,20,8,value(PDeg),0,0) screen.drawLine(W/2-PStep,H-Hpos+8,W/2-PStep,H-Hpos+4) if not NM then ssC(RR,GG,BB) else ssC(200,200,0) end screen.drawLine(W/2-PStep+StepPix/2,H-Hpos+8,W/2-PStep+StepPix/2,H-Hpos+6) screen.drawLine(W/2-PStep-StepPix/2,H-Hpos+8,W/2-PStep-StepPix/2,H-Hpos+6) for i=1,mc(W/StepPix) do sdTB(W/2-PStep-i*StepPix-10,H-Hpos-3,20,8,value(PDeg-i*Step),0,0) screen.drawLine(W/2-PStep-i*StepPix,H-Hpos+8,W/2-PStep-i*StepPix,H-Hpos+4) if not NM then ssC(RR,GG,BB) else ssC(200,200,0) end screen.drawLine(W/2-PStep-i*StepPix-StepPix/2,H-Hpos+8,W/2-PStep-i*StepPix-StepPix/2,H-Hpos+6) end
ssC(200,0,0)
screen.drawTriangleF(W/2-3,H-Hpos+9,W/2+4,H-Hpos+9,W/2,H-Hpos+5)
end end
function round(Value) a,b=math.modf(Value) if b>=0.5 then return a+1 else return a end end
function value(V) if V>360 then V=V-360 elseif V<0 then V=360+V end
if V==360 or V==0 then return "N" elseif V==90 then return "O" elseif V==180 then return "S" elseif V==270 then return "W" else if not NM then ssC(RR,GG,BB) else ssC(0,200,0) end return sf("%.0f",V) end end

function onDraw() w=screen.getWidth() h=screen.getHeight() radiusOfCircle = 9 angle = (number*4)-2 rPoint = rotatePoint(ypos, xpos, angle, ypos-radiusOfCircle, xpos) sC(200,0,0) dL(xpos,ypos,rPoint.y,rPoint.x) dStr(xpos-4, ypos+3, sF("%03.0f",data)) sC(0,255,0) drawArc(xpos,ypos,9,-130,90) sC(0,100,0) dTx(xpos-8,ypos+9,label) sC(0,255,0) dL(xpos,ypos+1,xpos+10,ypos)
end
function rotatePoint(cx, cy, angle, px, py) s = si(angle) c = math.cos(angle) px = px - cx py = py - cy xnew = px * c + py * s ynew = py * c - px * s x = xnew + cx y = ynew + cy return {x=x, y=y} end
